reviewHighlightsFromGuests.commentV2: My stay at Karuna Villa was absolutely wonderful , one of the best parts was that all the major visiting sites were nearby, making it super easy to explore . I highly recommend staying here , youll feel welcomed, relaxed, and well taken care of. Thank you Preeti, for being such an amazing host. Looking forward to coming back soon!

translation.comments: My stay at Karuna Villa was absolutely wonderful , one of the best parts was that all the major visiting sites were nearby, making it super easy to explore . I highly recommend staying here , youll feel welcomed, relaxed, and well taken care of. Thank you Preeti, for being such an amazing host. Looking forward to coming back soon!

reviewHighlightsFromGuests.commentV2: Preeti's place was v nice, meticulous , clean, peaceful, surrounded by greenery. Caretaker Mangal was v helpful even at odd hrs like 3am. Owner Ms Preeti was just a call away. It was v near to d conference venue Deendayal hastkala sankul and so was v convenient though far from Vishwanath temple and old city. Overall stay was good.

reviewHighlightsFromGuests.commentV2:
We had a pleasant stay at this place. The caretaker was very active in solving any issues. The bathroom was clean. 
Deendayal Hasthkala Sankul is nearby, walking distance. The stay was well lit by sunlight. Will definitely visit and stay again when I visit Varanasi. Thank you for making our stay memorable.
